Package com.flowpowered.react.collision.shape

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AABB
    Represents a bounding volume of type "Axis Aligned Bounding Box".
    BoxShape
    Represents a 3D box shape.
    CapsuleShape
    Represents a capsule collision shape that is defined around the Y axis.
    CollisionShape
    Represents the collision shape associated with a body that is used during the narrow-phase collision detection.
    ConeShape
    Represents a cone collision shape centered at the origin and aligned with the Y axis.
    ConvexMeshShape
    This class represents a convex mesh shape.
    CylinderShape
    Represents a cylinder collision shape around the Y axis and centered at the origin.
    SphereShape
    Represents a sphere collision shape that is centered at the origin and defined by its radius.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CollisionShape.CollisionShapeType
    An enumeration of the possible collision shape (box, sphere, cone and cylinder).
